          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-1" n="1">A widow kept a favourite cat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-2" n="2">At first a gentle creature</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-3" n="3">But w<hi rend="superscript">n</hi>: he was grown sleik, and fat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-4" n="4">W<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>: many a mouse &amp; many a rat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-5" n="5">He soon disclos'd his nature.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-6" n="6">The fox &amp; he were friends of old</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-7" n="7">Nor cou'd they now be parted</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-8" n="8">They nightly slunk to rob y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Fold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-9" n="9">Devour'd y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Lambs y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Fleeces sold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-10" n="10">And Puss grew Lion hearted.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-11" n="11">He scratch \<hi rend="italics">add</hi>·her\ maid, &amp; stole her cream,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-12" n="12">He tore her best lac'd pinner</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-13" n="13">Nor Chanticleer upon y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> beam</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-14" n="14">Nor chick, nor Duckling scapes w<hi rend="superscript">n</hi>: grim</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-15" n="15">Invites y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Fox to dinner.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-16" n="16">The Dame full wisely did decree,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-17" n="17">For fear he shoud dispatch more,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-18" n="18">y<hi rend="superscript">ṭ</hi> y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> false wretch shoud worried be</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-19" n="19">But in a sawcy manner he</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-20" n="20">Thus speech'd it like a Lechmore.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-21" n="21">Must I against all right &amp; law,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-22" n="22">Like Pole-cat vile be treated</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-23" n="23">I who so long w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>: tooth &amp; claw,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-24" n="24">Have kept domestick mice in awe,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-25" n="25">And foreign rats defeated.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-26" n="26">Your golden pippins, and y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>: pyes</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-27" n="27">how oft have I defended</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-28" n="28">Tis true y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> pinner y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>: y<hi rend="superscript">u</hi>: prise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-29" n="29">I tore in frolick to your eyes</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-30" n="30">I never harm intended.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-31" n="31">I am a cat of honour, stay</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-32" n="32">Quoth she no longer parly</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-33" n="33">W<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>: ere y<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>: did in battle slay</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-34" n="34">By law of arms became y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>: prey</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-35" n="35">I hope y<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>: won it fairly.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-36" n="36">Of this we grant y<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>: stand acquit</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-37" n="37">But not of y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>: outrages</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-38" n="38">Tell me perfidious was it fitt</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-39" n="39">To make my cream a perquisite</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-40" n="40">And steal to mend y<hi rend="superscript">or</hi>: wages</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-41" n="41">So flagrant is thy insolence</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-42" n="42">So vile thy breach of trust is</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-43" n="43">That longer w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>: thee to dispence</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-44" n="44">Were want of power, want of sence</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-153-009D-line-45" n="45">Here towser do him justice.</l>
          </lg>
